lenders.loan_because: The Healthy Vibe believes strongly in Community. Community is defined as “a group of people living together in one place”. The world is one large community and everyone deserves an equal opportunity to create a life they love. Living here in Newfoundland, Canada, we are surrounded by opportunity. Therefore, we wanted to reach beyond our land and extend a hand up to those who are looking for opportunity to grow and add value to their communities.
lenders.occupational_info: We aim to inspire and empower our customers with the knowledge and guidance they need to take a proactive approach to achieving their own 'Healthy Vibe'. By creating a fun, educational and encouraging environment within our stores, online communities and through our strategic partnerships and alliances, we provide our customers with the opportunities to grow and share their knowledge while easily finding quality natural health care products and services that are delivered with excellent customer service.

The idea of micro-loans, helping others to sort out their own situation, rather than sorting it out for them, looks consistent with the ideas we promote for creating better workplaces. 

In the Scrum framework people are given the opportunity to manage their own work and they are offered any assistance they need as they figure out together how to create a great workplace and amazing products.

In this account we deposit any surplus we get from non-profit events such as out pro-bono Professional Scrum Foundations training for students (we charge a small fee for these, to cover materials and make sure people show up)
lenders.occupational_info: Trying to assist others to create greater places to work at and to create new amazing products.
